description:
Original analog and digital clock looks like watch. You can set it as application, Live Wallpaper or widget. The clock supports 12/24 time format and display the current date according to installed language.

Options:
 * Clock size;
 * Background color;
 * Show date, month, day of the week, battery charge. Move slot to desired place;
 * Show digital clock;
 * Show second hand;
 * Five kinds of fonts;
 * Align the clock on the Home screen;
 * Time to speech by double tap or periodically;
 * Keep screen on for app.
